Hey, take it easy.

806
00:40:12,720 --> 00:40:14,040
This stuff's pretty strong.

807
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:15,080
Switch to water.

808
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:16,880
- Get me a glass of water.
- Sure.

809
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:20,640
- Thank you.
- You are welcome.

810
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:27,960
I'm sorry.

811
00:40:29,280 --> 00:40:31,680
I lost control of my emotions earlier.

812
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:32,880
But

813
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:35,360
I know you were just looking out for me.

814
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:38,320
Li Jinyu,

815
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:42,440
why do you always
control your emotions so tightly?

816
00:40:43,480 --> 00:40:44,560
I wish

817
00:40:44,640 --> 00:40:46,280
you'd stop boxing yourself in

818
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,960
with all these rules.

819
00:40:51,120 --> 00:40:53,000
Sometimes, you should
let yourself go wild.

820
00:40:55,240 --> 00:40:57,600
Not everyone is qualified for that.

821
00:41:13,920 --> 00:41:14,800
Li Jinyu,

822
00:41:16,520 --> 00:41:18,560
if anyone ever tells you

823
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:21,200
you're not qualified,

824
00:41:22,160 --> 00:41:23,320
send them to me.

825
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:25,920
From now on,

826
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:29,520
let me conquer the world for you.

827
00:41:46,280 --> 00:41:51,400
<i>Your eyes</i>

828
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:57,240
<i>Like shooting stars in the night</i>

829
00:41:59,720 --> 00:42:05,520
<i>Streaking across frozen borders</i>

830
00:42:06,720 --> 00:42:09,680
<i>To pierce my heart's defenses</i>

831
00:42:09,760 --> 00:42:14,760
<i>Just like that, conquered</i>

832
00:42:16,280 --> 00:42:18,960
<i>A black goldfish</i>

833
00:42:19,800 --> 00:42:25,120
<i>Stranded in desert sands</i>

834
00:42:27,240 --> 00:42:33,320
<i>Even if all memories fade</i>

835
00:42:33,920 --> 00:42:36,720
<i>Your silhouette lingers</i>

836
00:42:37,480 --> 00:42:39,880
<i>Etched in my mind</i>

837
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:44,320
<i>Every time I gaze at you, longing to near</i>

838
00:42:44,400 --> 00:42:46,840
<i>I drown, unasked, in reverie</i>

839
00:42:46,920 --> 00:42:51,040
<i>Those accidental heartbeats</i>

840
00:42:51,120 --> 00:42:53,120
<i>How could I ever discard them?</i>

841
00:42:53,200 --> 00:42:57,600
<i>If you sensed my turmoil, my retreat</i>

842
00:42:57,680 --> 00:43:00,360
<i>Know it's only because I care too deeply</i>

843
00:43:00,440 --> 00:43:04,360
<i>The courage I threw away</i>

844
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:07,960
<i>Where does it hide now?</i>

845
00:43:08,040 --> 00:43:13,680
<i>With the last of my strength</i>
<i>I'd reach to hold you</i>

846
00:43:14,440 --> 00:43:16,040
<i>Don't you dare doubt it</i>

